n to transform medicine. </p><div class="jelpepe jelpep0"><span><span class="_1g89o322 _19wv7tc5"><span><span>Robert Hart</span></span></span></span><span class="duet--article--timestamp g4xafw2 g4xafw0 _19wv7tc5 _1044qizs"><time dateTime="2026-07-03T11:49:10+00:00">Jul 3</time></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="duet--layout--river-container _9kze5z0"><div class="_9kze5z1"><div class="duet--layout--river x96f282 x96f281"><div class="duet--layout--page-header bpecqn0 bpecqn1"><div class="bpecqni bpecqnf"><h2 class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup bpecqnn bpecqnm _19wv7tc2">Latest In AI</h2></div><div class="sticky-nav-trigger"></div></div><div class="x96f283"><div><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card duet--content-cards--quick-post rj2ep84 rj2ep89" role="article"><a aria-label="Leaked video shows Microsoft’s work on a lightweight ‘Copilot OS’ built for AI." class="rj2ep88" href="/tech/961195/microsoft-copilot-os-aion-leak"></a><div class="rj2ep81"><div class="rj2ep87"><div class="_1jiz7rn0 _1jiz7rn1"><div class="_1jiz7rn7"><img alt="Richard Lawler" data-chromatic="ignore" loading="lazy" width="34" height="34" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="_4aoxp34" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/01/RICHARD_BLURPLE.jpg?quality=90&amp;strip=all&amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100&amp;w=48 1x, https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/01/RICHARD_BLURPLE.jpg?quality=90&amp;strip=all&amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100&amp;w=96 2x" src="https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/01/RICHARD_BLURPLE.jpg?quality=90&amp;strip=all&amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100&amp;w=96"/></div><div class="_1jiz7rn2 _1jiz7rn3"><span class="_1jiz7rn6">Richard Lawler</span><span class="duet--article--timestamp g4xafw2 g4xafw0 _19wv7tc5 _1jiz7rna"><time dateTime="2026-07-02T23:54:43+00:00">Jul 2</time></span></div></div><div class="_4ine551 _4ine550"><div class="_4ine5